.RS 4
.IP
.nf
\f[C]
virgil\ encrypt\ \-i\ plain.txt\ \-o\ plain.txt.venc\ email:bob\@domain.com\ email:tom\@domain.com
\f[]
.fi
.RE
.IP "3." 3
Alice encrypts the data with a password:
.RS 4
.IP
.nf
\f[C]
virgil\ encrypt\ \-i\ plain.txt\ \-o\ plain.txt.venc\ pass:strong_password
\f[]
.fi
.RE
